oracle.spatial.spark.vector.geoenrichment

Interface SpatialFeature

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public interface SpatialFeature
extends java.io.Serializable
    Represents a feature from a spatial data layer. The feature is expected to have at least an id, a geometry and the name of the spatial data layer where it belongs to.
    If the feature contains more properties, these are stored in the properties map.
    Author:
    hsaucedo
